                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.00/5406: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Vice Consul at Viborg</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Imbrie</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Viborg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-10-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 16, 1919</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[Received October 17, 1:57 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>116. Under cover of fire from British fleet, Russian troops are being landed in
                    neighborhood of Krasnaya Gorka with capture of that fort as objective. White
                    advance continues; their troops are within ten versts of Gatchina the capture of
                    which is expected today. Bolsheviks morale [apparent omission] their retreat at
                    times becoming a rout.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Imbrie</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
